reviews.review_text: sloppy show esp s2 1st set is pretty good, but honestly s2 is quite sloppy, gasping for air. Yes, a good deal of 84 has that 'junky' kind of delivery and is still great, but this one just isn't as good as many others in the period.

energy Many say this show is not as good as others during this year. I wil say the energy on this night was over the top. Maybe cause was 1st show of the tour or maybe just location. I happen to  really enjoy this show on the day it was played live. I was half way between the board and the stage and I remember the crowd loving it. 
I would give it a 4 just because I think the energy means alot to a show. Also add the fact that I am from the east coast and  I prefer the west coast style of energy this had that type of feel to it to me that is
